{"tid":52009,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【最後的一餐】死囚行刑前 究竟會揀食啲乜？","createTime":"2016-12-23T16:41:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T23:48:19.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a62ede63eada5a8932e437cce37bdf2be394e6c6","tid":52009,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:41:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161222/56073717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161222%2F56073717&d=UEqiDeshdO8W%2BcbXLZcSCoscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=0da4b4be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161222%2F56073717&h=a1a49f3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161222/56073717</a><br />\n<br />\n美國大部份死囚臨行刑前，都會選擇享用特別餐－－任意揀選想吃的東西，之後才上路。有攝影師就重現本年已行刑死囚的最後一餐，希望藉此引起公眾關注死刑問題。 <br />\n本年大多數死囚也把握最後機會享用美食，而牛扒是他們「最後一餐」的大熱選擇。例如一位在7月行刑的死囚，就選擇了三成熟肉眼扒伴焗薯及沙律，配以蒜蓉包及可樂，更點了檸檬蛋白批作甜品，甚為「刁鑽」。有人就簡單一點，只是點一份牛扒飯或意粉就足夠。 <br />\n薄餅就是緊隨牛扒的熱門選擇，有死囚沒甚麼特別要求，只要一份大薄餅就於願足矣；亦有人想同時吃到牛肉及薄餅，於是另外要求一個牛肉芝士餡餅，並配上釀蘑菇及沙律。 <br />\n然而有死囚卻沒有心情選擇最後一餐的食物，只是享用傳統的「最後一餐」－－香煎雞扒飯或肉餅飯伴雜豆等等。 <br />\n出生於紐西蘭的食品攝影師哈格里夫斯（Henry Hargreaves），早於2011年已拍攝同類照片，今年的作品是他的續作。他是參考了20位死囚的資料，再重新擺出他們的最後一餐再作拍攝。哈格里夫斯指美國1976年重啟死刑以來，每年平均有47人受刑，但不少案件其實仍有疑點，隨時冤枉好人，遂希望作品可以喚起大眾對死刑的關注。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161221/large/1482310659_0013.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161221%2Flarge%2F1482310659_0013.jpg&h=fc1ac2cb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161221/large/1482300009_d794.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161221%2Flarge%2F1482300009_d794.jpg&h=4643adc9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161221/large/1482300010_ad9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161221%2Flarge%2F1482300010_ad9b.jpg&h=ece42d1f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161221/large/1482300012_4da7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161221%2Flarge%2F1482300012_4da7.jpg&h=511df7fe&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161221/large/1482306253_f475.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161221%2Flarge%2F1482306253_f475.jpg&h=b49ba439&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161221/large/1482316754_7825.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161221%2Flarge%2F1482316754_7825.jpg&h=9452708c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161221/large/1482316756_5c91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161221%2Flarge%2F1482316756_5c91.jpg&h=eb89919e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fed86c6ab330abfd253c7812e550e94b403d1cc8","tid":52009,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:59:15.000Z","msg":"尾二個樣好得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6848505c0268a242cd287eda54c7f79dd801423a","tid":52009,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T21:34:00.000Z","msg":"第一個咁好笑容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728da1c8a68489b06134056507d275d8590a48f4","tid":52009,"uid":6238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":